2.0 of 5 bubbles
Halong dream - not
We are just back from a brilliant Vietnam holiday. We went to stunning Halong Bay and did a three day two night package with Hai Long Junks - discoverhalong.

It was the most disappointing experience. Our two night three day trip was really two one night trips put together.
After night one we were taken off our comfortable junk onto an uncomfortable boat to chug around for the day to the sound of a diesel engine while our comfortable boat and luggage went back to port to pick up the next lot of tourists.
We met our boat that afternnoon with new shipmates at an attraction we had done the day before.. essentially repeating our tour.
We then requested to go out in Canoes ... 20USD and we were allowed no time to go.
Halong Bay is beautiful with the 600+ diesel boats chugging around ...but don't waste your time or money with this company doing the two night trip ... not worth it.
Written September 19, 2007
